    ControlsMenu

    EventHandler
    Event Handler object that runs whenever an objects generates an event
    GameMenu
    An in game menu that pauses the game by taking control of the game loop
    HighscoreMenu
    A highscore menu that reads the most recent highscores and displays them on the screen

    The main menu of the game.
    PlayerDiedMenu
    The menu to show when the player has been killed.Displays their current time and a button to take them back to the main menu

    SettingsMenu
    The settings menu.
